description: Lists the connectors for the specified Region.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: Returns a token that you can use to call ListConnectors again and receive additional results, if there are any.

nested_items.name: Connectors
nested_items.description: Returns an array, where each item contains the details of a connector.

nested_items.name: Arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the specified connector.

nested_items.name: ConnectorId
nested_items.description: The unique identifier for the connector.

nested_items.name: Url
nested_items.description: The URL of the partner's AS2 or SFTP endpoint.
